title: Craig Hulet Coast to Coast May 3, 2016
description:
Coast to Coast May 3, 2016 Current Events - Craig Hulet

In the first half, analyst of geopolitics and foreign policy Craig B. Hulet comments on the election cycle and current events. Followed in the second half by Midweek Open Lines.

News segment guests: John M. Curtis, Howard Bloom, Robert Zimmerman
